column1: My husband and I stayed from June 18th to the 21st. We could not have asked for better. The room was super quiet, clean and nice sized and the staff was superb. Everyone was so helpful. Especially the concierge Jonathan. He got us on the OnBoard Night tour which was worth every penny. He also recommended restaurants and made an easy to understand and navigate map. He truly made our trip even better. We would absolutely stay here again and again. The metro station across from the hotel made travel simple. Don't hesitate booking here. You won't regret it!!!
